 build instructions (with cmake):
 -------------------------------- 
 
 $ mkdir build
 $ cd build
 $ cmake ..
 $ make install

 To build the gear tests you should also set BUILD_GEAR_TESTS=ON
 For this replace step 3 in the instructions above with:
 $ cmake -DBUILD_GEAR_TESTS=ON ..

 
 For more information on CMake for the ILCSoftware check:
 http://www-flc.desy.de/ilcsoft (will be available soon!)

 CMake's official website:
 http://www.cmake.org
 

 
 build instructions (with ant): -> Deprecated, please use cmake!
 ---------------------------------------------------------------

 modify the env.sh  ( path to java ! ) and then source it:

  . env.sh

 ant aid.generate
 ant cpp
 ant cpp.doc   

 ---------------------------------------------------------------


 run the example ( ./src/cpp/test/testgear.cc )

  ./bin/testgear gear_ldc.xml
 

